@startuml si2.2-create-pending-maintenance-plan
title SI2.2 Create pending maintenance plan

start
:Receive selected-plan request;

if (selected plan request valid?) then ([Yes])
  :Load customer, equipment, and offering;
  :Lock selected offering price;
  :Create pending maintenance plan;
  :Produce business event
Pending maintenance plan created; <<sendSignal>>
  :Return success;
  stop
else ([No])
  :Return selected-plan validation failure
(offering-not-found, offering-unavailable,
offering-not-applicable, or duplicate-plan);
  stop
endif

@enduml
